name: The Brunswick Chair
description: The Brunswick is a perfect representation of DAVIDSON's superlative design and craft expertise. A luxury occasional, desk or dining chair, whose shimmering profile captivates in its originality. Finished in a dark-tinted beech, the legs both complement and contrast with the lustrous body in fabric from Armani Casa. The wing-shaped backrest, alongside the crisp lines of the armrests, create a silhouette that is as inviting as it is impressive. As with other DAVIDSON chairs, the Brunswick can be upholstered in a range of fabrics or leathers to suit your interior.
